{"tid":1437560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於鏡片防霧, 要用防霧劑。","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:42:29.000Z","uid":297672,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6314228c3f929794c90f822566a84a6f3ae448","tid":1437560,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"有游水朋友同我講, 屌啲咩鏡片本身防霧大多數係廢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢自己就會用防霧劑嘅。<br />\n<br />\n咁佢幫我搽咗個防霧劑之後呢, 嘩屌真係新世界! 未試過原來係可以睇得咁清晰, 游幾個鐘都冇霧, 唔駛成日除鏡擦一擦。<br />\n<br />\n教學:<br />\n1 放入池沖一沖副鏡<br />\n2 將防霧劑塗上鏡片內側<br />\n3 放入池又再沖一沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鏡片起霧好危險, 游夜水能見度會降低, 有堆人向住你游都未必睇到, 好危險。少少錢唔好慳。"},{"pid":"1d1f2bb957ed4728c9afb4a90406c604a6e61c83","tid":1437560,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"開錯台shit"},{"pid":"df68c3908ed8f3d4c120fd9427a79b591f2b88fc","tid":1437560,"uid":73310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1f2bb957ed4728c9afb4a90406c604a6e61c83","tid":1437560,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"開錯台shit"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"邊到買？"},{"pid":"73a3ef6990b1ca1f78ee02cf6541d6c1f7b2efaf","tid":1437560,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"囗水"},{"pid":"1dfe226b75c3a4ef2d326206ff92703b33e98344","tid":1437560,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"游開水表示 自己覺得搽到好過噴到"},{"pid":"bedd87e127dbc230c0f06d84b0c1db43e685a1b4","tid":1437560,"uid":224731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df68c3908ed8f3d4c120fd9427a79b591f2b88fc","tid":1437560,"uid":73310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1f2bb957ed4728c9afb4a90406c604a6e61c83","tid":1437560,"uid":297